title: 'Well-Made Acrylic Wool Sweater'
body: First time buying from this company and very pleased with the outcome! This wool sweater is just fantastic! It looks great, feels great, and is priced great! It didn't shrink too much (but it did shrink just a tiny bit) when I washed it. More importantly, for me, it didn't fade in it's color or design. It still looks as vibrant as the day I bought it.
